    "testimonials_TkkKtN": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_JWe9qz": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>I was unsure about spending nearly €120 on a pair of sandals and a summer dress from a brand I hadn’t ordered from before, but I’m genuinely delighted I gave it a chance. The quality was far better than I expected and everything arrived beautifully wrapped as well. The sandals are wonderfully comfortable and the dress fits perfectly for the warmer weather. I’ve since placed another order and I’m just as pleased.</p>",
            "author": "Bríd C.",
            "author_info": "Clonakilty, Cork"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_nanhC8": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>The parcel arrived much quicker than I expected, only a few days to Waterford, and everything was packed with great care. The cardigan feels wonderfully made and like it will last for years.</p>",
            "author": "Siobhán K.",
            "author_info": "Waterford City, Waterford"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_NqheJw": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>I had to contact customer support regarding sizing before ordering and they were incredibly helpful and patient. The blouse fits beautifully and is very comfortable to wear.</p>",
            "author": "Deirdre P.",
            "author_info": "Ballsbridge, Dublin"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_hpPQif": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>After wearing the trousers regularly for several months now, I can honestly say they’ve held up beautifully. The stitching is still perfect, the fabric hasn’t lost its shape at all, and they remain as comfortable as the day they arrived. Proper long-lasting clothing is difficult to come by nowadays.</p>",
            "author": "Gráinne W.",
            "author_info": "Kilkenny City, Kilkenny"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_J7NmE6": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>What struck me first was how lovely the presentation was when the package arrived. Everything was folded neatly and the material felt substantial straight away. The dress itself is elegant without being fussy and you can tell real care has gone into making it. I’ve already had compliments the few times I’ve worn it.</p>",
            "author": "Aoife T.",
            "author_info": "Ennis, Clare"
          }
        }
      },
