          "settings": {
            "code": "<h2>30-DAY MONEY-BACK GUARANTEE</h2>\n<p>We hope you feel truly happy with your order. If something is not quite right, you can return it within 30 days for a full refund. Simple, reassuring, and made to give you peace of mind when shopping with us.</p>",
